\begin_inset space \thinspace{}
\end_inset

µm.
 The objects outside of this aperture need to have some dimension defined,
 but it will be ignored as long as the outer radius of each layer is equal
 (we set it to 10
\begin_inset space \thinspace{}
\end_inset

µm).
